    "Federate any workload, any ML framework, and any programming language.",
    "Flower is an FL framework that offers a stable language and ML framework-agnostic implementation of an FL system.",
    "Flower provides an API wrapper for TensorFlow, TensorFlow Lite, PyTorch, PyTorch Lightning, Hugging Face, MXNet, JAX, and Scikit-Learn.",
    "-The framework allows for the rapid transition of existing ML training pipelines into an FL setup to evaluate their convergence properties and training time in a federated setting.",
